# Sink directory for paren-fuzz CI-defer runs (SCENARIOS §5.2).
# TestParenOracleFuzz writes <timestamp>.txt here when run with
# PAREN_FUZZ_DEFER=1 and a new mismatch is discovered. Human triage
# moves the entry into testdata/paren-fuzz-corpus/known-mismatches.txt
# (if it's a known-acceptable divergence) or triggers a parser fix
# (if it's a regression), then deletes the deferred file.
